      <title>大亨陈江和旗下金鹰集团子公司利用新可持续融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tycoon-tanoto-owned-rge-units-turn-to-sustainable-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼大亨陈江和 (Sukanto Tanoto) 旗下的新加坡皇家金鹰集团 (Royal Golden Eagle) 旗下子公司目前正在申请与可持续发展相关的贷款，该集团旨在将融资转向环保领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tycoon-tanoto-owned-rge-units-turn-to-sustainable-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称日本大型银行将寻求大幅削减日本央行债券购买规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/boj-sounds-out-market-players-before-finalizing-bond-buying-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据与会人士透露，日本最大的几家银行在央行市场参与者听证会上呼吁日本央行大幅削减每月债券购买量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/boj-sounds-out-market-players-before-finalizing-bond-buying-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 00:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔上任前美国股市或再试新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向国会作证以寻找美国利率前景的线索，美国股市周二有望再创历史新高。]]></description>
